WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.569
Hey, you.

2
00:00:03.569 --> 00:00:09.289
Do you have an MBA or a Master's?

3
00:00:09.289 --> 00:00:12.289
Lindsey, she'll be the new project coordinator.

4
00:00:12.289 --> 00:00:15.289
Um, James, she's only been at the company for two months.

5
00:00:15.289 --> 00:00:22.989
You heard me. Get her brief.

6
00:00:22.989 --> 00:00:25.989
What is this job at? Am I even qualified?

7
00:00:25.989 --> 00:00:28.989
No one's been qualified for this position.

8
00:00:28.989 --> 00:00:33.990
The last person had an MBA, and the person before that a PhD, and they're all gone.

9
00:00:33.990 --> 00:00:36.759
Do your homework.

10
00:00:36.759 --> 00:00:49.140
This is James Thompson, CEO of Thompson Pharmaceuticals.

